{"tid":1176980,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)經期隊長 五路追殺令 邊個殺我隻狗1-2","createTime":"2019-05-29T14:03:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-29T19:16:25.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c207162d9171b1c498978872afbd5ec8afdeef98","tid":1176980,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T14:03:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=DJJewhOFhIMK5JRdM%2BI1LkcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=d90dc28e\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=DJJewhOFhIMK5JRdM%2BI1LkcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=4f328f17\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=DJJewhOFhIMK5JRdM%2BI1LkcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=2209948a\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.char.tw/uploads/20190306062205_61.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.char.tw%2Fuploads%2F20190306062205_61.jpg&h=47c9dabf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://kalselpos.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/Captain-Marvel-001.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkalselpos.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F02%2FCaptain-Marvel-001.jpg&h=f3821f0a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://joseph-morris.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/captain-marvel-gif-7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fjoseph-morris.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2Fcaptain-marvel-gif-7.gif&h=3930e186&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/c/c5/Smokin-poster2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fc%2Fc5%2FSmokin-poster2.jpg&h=c5c9970f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DYuhXZ_XkAIuNVm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDYuhXZ_XkAIuNVm.jpg&h=62ceec90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.1995年，克里帝國星際部隊成員佛斯在首都哈拉星進行訓練，她困惑於被清除記憶而難以控制自身情緒及能量，所屬部隊指揮官楊羅格與克里AI統治者「至高智慧」因此不斷告誡教誨她。楊羅格的部隊受命前往邊境星球托法星，試圖尋找失蹤的克里人臥底，卻掉入敵對的史克魯爾人所設下的圈套。佛斯被史克魯爾人將軍塔洛斯擄走，楊羅格與其他成員被逼撤退。史克魯爾人在太空船內以記憶讀取裝置收集佛斯腦中的情報，使她回想起片段的零碎記憶。佛斯用超能力脫困成功並試圖逃離，最後她所乘的逃生艙被塔洛斯攻擊毀損，從太空墜至鄰近星球C-53（地球）<br />\n<br />\n2.命在旦夕的黑幫老大懸賞百萬賞金捉拿叛徒巴弟，各路殺手衝著賞金便躍躍欲試，掌握情資的FBI探員必須保護汙點證人巴弟的生命以起訴黑幫老大；各方使盡暗算心機，在賭城展開一場亂鬥<br />\n<br />\n3.約翰&middot;維克是一位退隱江湖的殺手，不久前失去了因病而逝的妻子海倫，這令他哀傷不已，舉辦完葬禮後連過去同為殺手的馬克斯也前來關心他。不久後，約翰收到了一隻海倫生前為他訂的小狗黛西，海倫希望黛西能陪伴約翰，而他也將黛西視為朋友。一早，約翰開著他69年的福特野馬愛車和黛西出門，當到一間加油站加油時，塔拉索夫家族的領頭維果的兒子約謝夫想要和約翰買下他的車，但被約翰拒絕，約謝夫便此心生不滿。當晚，約謝夫和另外兩位朋友格雷戈里、維克多蒙面闖入約翰家中，不但襲擊了他還殺死了黛西..<br />\n<br />\n4.在前殺手約翰&middot;維克殺光維果和約謝夫&middot;塔拉索夫一行人的四天後，約翰開始尋找自己遭到前者搶走的1969年福特野馬，並循跡發現車在維果的弟弟艾倫那裡。約翰在獲得艾倫根據地的門卡後隨即開車前往，並與艾倫的手下們展開飛車追逐及搏鬥，而艾倫也察覺到傳說中「殺神」的到來；在他打倒其手下後，約翰到艾倫的辦公室倒了兩杯酒給他，以示「和平」。接著約翰便開車回家，與自己在殺死維果後帶回家的「沒有取名」狗見面..<br />\n<br />\n10 15PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=DJJewhOFhIMK5JRdM%2BI1LkcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=3cdc8f82\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=DJJewhOFhIMK5JRdM%2BI1LkcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=8ae5f53f\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"038e4202690115c72fe503e51c9db10ace766acf","tid":1176980,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T14:04:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8678c6715e0c9fc35d79ecf9d5c4a2af5a9a141","tid":1176980,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T14:22:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"292d8f028625ab74c495af130ba4e03dd7f9fc5f","tid":1176980,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T15:28:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"658cc22442ec54c5725923f290ab0dec6ecdcdc7","tid":1176980,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T16:21:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c42505839dd94721d9f586cb4e7fc53083e83d0","tid":1176980,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T17:15:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\